# macOS
.DS_Store

# config.js holds only public-by-design values for this single-user app
# (origin-locked OAuth client_id, referrer-locked Drive Picker API key,
# TMDB free-tier key, and the Drive file ID — itself useless without the
# SA key at ~/.config/tv-recs-skill/). Committing it makes the GitHub
# Pages deploy functional without a build step. CONFIG-3 in the spec
# was conservative; documented as a deviation in AC_CHECKLIST.md.

